Package ussr.physics.jme Description

A physics simulation implementation based on JME (JMonkeyEngine). Implements the interfaces defined in the ussr.physics package. Provides a collection of actuators and sensors as well as various utility classes. Concrete robots are defined in the ussr.physics.jme.robots package.
